      "id": "PHALA_6_15",
      "text": "गुरुचन्द्रयोः केन्द्रगते गजकेसरी योगो भवति",
      "transliteration": "Gurucandrayoḥ kendragate gajakesarī yogo bhavati",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When Jupiter and Moon are in kendras, Gajakesari Yoga is formed",
        "hi": "गुरु और चंद्र के केंद्र में होने पर गजकेसरी योग बनता है"
      },
      "source": {
        "text": "Phaladeepika",
